Package net.minecraftforge.network

Class LoginWrapper

java.lang.Object
net.minecraftforge.network.LoginWrapper
public class LoginWrapper extends Object
Wrapper for custom login packets. Transforms unnamed login channel messages into channels dispatched the same as regular custom packets.
